@baseUrl = http://localhost:5295
@token = your-jwt-token-here

### Health Check - Full System
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Health Check - Readiness
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/ready
Accept: application/json

### Health Check - Liveness
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/live
Accept: application/json

### Test Endpoint (Development Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/test
Accept: application/json

### Alumni Registration - Submit
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/alumni/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "staffNumber": "0012345",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "phoneNumber": "+254712345678",
  "department": "Engineering",
  "jobTitle": "Software Engineer",
  "yearsOfService": 5,
  "lastWorkingDate": "2024-01-15",
  "reasonForLeaving": "Retirement",
  "linkedInUrl": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/johndoe",
  "currentEmployer": "Tech Corp",
  "currentJobTitle": "Senior Engineer",
  "stayConnected": true
}

### Alumni Registration - Verify Email
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/alumni/verify?token=verification-token-here
Accept: application/json

### Admin - Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@kenya-airways.com",
  "password": "your-password"
}

### Admin - Get All Registrations (Requires Auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/registrations?pageNumber=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Admin - Approve Registration (Requires Auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/registrations/{id}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Admin - Reject Registration (Requires Auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/registrations/{id}/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Incomplete information"
}
